data.text: From the private autograph collections of Fred/Toni/Ed (as described on the home page) who bought autographs from celebrities for decades, especially at cowboy western film festivals. All autographs will be shipped in the pages of a thick complimentary convention program guide/magazine to ensure additional protection. Please open the magazine to find your autographs inside. (We have thousands of these Nostalgia magazines to give away so you get one free with your purchase.) Purchase three or more autographs and pay no postage. 30 day return policy. After 30 days, all sales final. If you have any questions, please do not hesitate to contact me. All autographs sold on a first come, first serve basis.
